power-about-the-same-as-your-computer-monitor.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-human-brain-runs-on-20-watts-of-power-about-the-same-as-your-computer-monitor</guid></item><item><title>新型4D视觉芯片可帮助机器人同时追踪距离和速度</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-4d-vision-chip-can-help-robots-track-distance-and-speed-at-once</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:11:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-4d-vision-chip-can-help-robots-track-distance-and-speed-at-once</guid></item><item><title>逆向设计：定制功能聚合物的新途径</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/inverse-design-a-new-pathway-to-custom-functional-polymers</link><description>在一次聚餐中，你吃到了最好的巧克力曲奇饼——金黄色、厚实、耐嚼。不幸的是，您不知道谁制作了饼干来获取食谱，因此您决定重新创建它。使用正向设计原则，您可以从数十个选项中随机选择一个食谱，烘烤并观察生成的饼干。如果它们太薄，您可以重新开始新的食谱，添加更多面粉或将面团冷却更长时间并制作新一批。另一种方法是从您想要的饼干特性开始并询问：什么配方和烘焙设置可以生产出这种类型的饼干？这种方法称为逆向设计。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/inverse-design-a-new-pathway-to-custom-functional-polymers.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/inverse-design-a-new-pathway-to-custom-functional-polymers</guid></item><item><title>德克萨斯州航天公司开发用于月球车建造月球基地的施工工具</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/texas-space-firm-developing-construction-tools-for-rovers-to-build-moon-base</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/texas-space-firm-developing-construction-tools-for-rovers-to-build-moon-base</guid></item><item><title>Nvidia 表示可以在不改变模型权重的情况下将 LLM 内存缩小 20 倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nvidia-says-it-can-shrink-llm-memory-20x-without-changing-model-weights</link><description>Nvidia 的 KV 缓存转换编码 (KVTC) 在不更改模型的情况下将 LLM 键值缓存压缩了 20 倍，从而将多轮 AI 应用程序的 GPU 内存成本和首次令牌时间降低了 8 倍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nvidia-says-it-can-shrink-llm-memory-20x-without-changing-model-weights.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/nvidia-says-it-can-shrink-llm-memory-20x-without-changing-model-weights</guid></item><item><title>研究绘制了与活体大脑神经传递相关的基因活动</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/study-maps-gene-activity-linked-to-neurotransmission-in-living-brains</link><description>研究人员在活人大脑中发现了与神经传递相关的独特且可重复的基因表达程序，为支持人类认知、情感和行为的分子机制提供了前所未有的见解。研究结果发表于 2 月 19 日&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/study-maps-gene-activity-linked-to-neurotransmission-in-living-brains2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:11:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/study-maps-gene-activity-linked-to-neurotransmission-in-living-brains</guid></item><item><title>CO2渗流条件下花岗岩的力学响应及渗透率演化特征</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-mechanical-response-and-permeability-evolution-characteristics-of-granite-under-the-condition-of-co2-seepage</link><description>刚刚发布： &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-mechanical-response-and-permeability-evolution-characteristics-of-granite-under-the-condition-of-co2-seepage2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 22:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-mechanical-response-and-permeability-evolution-characteristics-of-granite-under-the-condition-of-co2-seepage</guid></item></channel></rss>